{"tid":1074124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又出軌... 西環電車出軌翻側 司機受傷","createTime":"2019-03-23T07:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T08:49:32.000Z","uid":32732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7df44d5eb1c316c1f69a4ba937c86d1fd75be97b","tid":1074124,"uid":32732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:26:41.000Z","msg":"西環凌晨發生電車翻側意外，一輛開往屈地街車廠的電車，行經一個右彎位時突告出軌，衝向左邊行人路，撞毀鐵欄、路牌及石柱，然後向右翻側，橫亘西行兩條行車線及行人路上。司機由途人協助救出，送院救治。警方及電車公司調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n現場德輔道西418號對開，凌晨零時，一輛西行往屈地街車廠的電車，車上已沒有乘客，幸當時沒有行人及車輛經過，否則後果嚴重。現場路上遺下20多米長刮花痕迹。<br />\n<br />\n目擊者稱，聽到隆然巨響，赫見電車翻側，司機一度被困，多名途人衝前協助將他救出，他腳部受傷送院，大批消防員到場救援。警方封鎖現場德輔道西調查。<br />\n<br />\n1904年通車至今共發生3宗罕見電車翻側事故，1964年4月，一輛電車在金鐘道轉一個急彎時出軌，撞向西行線另一輛電車後翻側，釀1死59傷。1983年10月，一輛電車在筲箕灣道近愛秩序灣道與一輛混凝土車相撞，兩車齊齊翻側，造成29人受傷，2017年4月6日，一輛電車在中環輔道中匯豐銀行總行對開彎位出軌，右車頭猛撼東行線的電車站，繼而向左翻側，造成14人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190323/59400933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190323%2F59400933&d=INFrb%2BpCZNVkt1J9J2ljEIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=ccf76db9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190323%2F59400933&h=e72d1bc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190323/59400933</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a7tumDb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa7tumDb.png&h=de6b07d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GQjtCbx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGQjtCbx.png&h=2c7835bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WSjQQwy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWSjQQwy.png&h=d4fbc978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港交通意外真係好鐘意一不離二..... 電車都炒...."},{"pid":"e0b403a97f5b558c4f763fec60ebf444c6002532","tid":1074124,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:48:02.000Z","msg":"Molamola"},{"pid":"9ce79c7601c1a4203ac9910084ccb58ebbeec265","tid":1074124,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:49:10.000Z","msg":"你頭先先起身?"},{"pid":"37b6d0ea697cc357ae74235fa997776f7267764f","tid":1074124,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:49:32.000Z","msg":"職安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}